 {"id":"bd-mblr.1.4","title":"Coverage SLOs and Quality Gate Policy","description":"Set explicit thresholds and policy: minimum line/branch/function coverage, mandatory real-backend tests for critical paths, and no-merge criteria. Define exceptions workflow and review ownership.","design":"Separate hard fail criteria from temporary allowlist mechanics so exceptions do not silently become permanent.","acceptance_criteria":"- Policy defines minimum line/branch/function thresholds and no-mock evidence requirements for critical invariants.
- Policy includes exception workflow with expiry, owner, and remediation deadline.
